headline: Winners And Losers Of Q1: Constellation Brands (NYSE:STZ) Vs The Rest Of The Beverages, Alcohol, and Tobacco Stocks
summary: The end of an earnings season can be a great time to discover new stocks and assess how companies are handling the current business environment. Let’s take a look at how Constellation Brands (NYSE:STZ) and the rest of the beverages, alcohol, and tobacco stocks fared in Q1.
